{"tid":1234370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「撐TVB」TVB真香港良心","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T03:43:24.000Z","uid":7782,"like":108,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7a14d733d091023264ef3d1b357eaac84ba1ae66","tid":1234370,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB我DLLM，以前嘅TVB已經死咗<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我係一個八十後，以前免費電視得TVB同ATV，細個成日屌ATV選擇性報導新聞。就算ATV曾經有過極少量出色節目都係撐TVB。<br />\n<br />\n八，九十年代，八十太細印象唔太清晰唔講...九十年代，放學睇「閃電傳真機」，夜晚睇大時代等等「經典神劇」太多套唔數，世界杯都要睇TVB聽阿叔同荷蘭叻講波，新聞就更加要睇TVB，因為以前ATV新聞會睇少好多嘢同覺得TVB比較中肯。<br />\n<br />\n真係撐TVB超過廿年，不過唔記得幾時開始就唔係點再睇.......因為變咗<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>CCTVB</strong></span></span>，節目質素都唔講，奶共奶到上晒腦，明明係曲嘅都編輯到變直，新聞更加DLLM，以前ATV最多唔播，CCTVB選擇性播放加選擇性編輯，DLLM咁我睇嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999, 家中兩老都係一直睇開「TVB」，但為免「CCTVB」繼續洗佢地腦，我用行動「說不」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個my tv super係用HKBN硬推俾我，如果要還我最多賠錢都唔俾佢洗兩老腦，如果HKBN係有利益俾CCTVB，我會考慮到期就轉其他！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68H3LwX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68H3LwX.png&h=372dc0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw，舊嘢係堅硬，好大力打咗好多下都係爆少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過d port爛咗已經夠！"},{"pid":"ebbb9944511d9379d97de4a79b9d8e4ef617fb83","tid":1234370,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21cece7bde4f04af54aca71ba6f7ac3f7d858050","tid":1234370,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ad66e02439781b9246469bae436896407d0d770","tid":1234370,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8db940e9c1254aae5d7925c26f0